					<p>
						Answers to many of your questions about MOFILM, our competitions and more!
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>What is MOFILM?</strong><br />MOFILM is a community for people who love being creative.
						We run competitions with leading brands and film festivals to showcase creativity helping your
						work to get noticed. We also distribute the best content all over the world helping our
						community to monetise their content.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>What are the benefits of joining the MOFILM Community?</strong><br />Our tagline is
						'Get Creative - Get Noticed - Get Famous!' and that's exactly what we provide to filmmakers all
						over the world. MOFILM is a platform to showcase your films, make money from them through our
						distribution links and enter competitions to meet famous filmmakers or come to one of our
						workshops, either virtual or for real as part of our MOFILM:Labs programme.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Which Celebrities have worked with MOFILM?</strong><br />To date we've worked with many
						leading filmmakers who love the MOFILM concept. These include Robert Redford, Kevin Spacey,
						Spike Lee, Isabella Rossellini, Dayton &amp; Faris (Little Miss Sunshine), Justin Lin
						(Fast &amp; the Furious: Tokyo Drift) and Cory McAbee (American Astronaut).
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>How do I get MOFILM on my mobile?</strong><br />Just go to
						<a href="http://www.mofilm.com">www.mofilm.com</a> on your mobile device. MOFILM is also available
						from the application store if you have an Apple iPhone, Google Android phone or Blackberry.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Will I be charged to watch MOFILMs?</strong><br />In most cases accessing our content is
						free. There are charges for some mobile applications and you may incur data transfer charges if
						you do not have free Internet access as part of your mobile tariff. Please check with your
						operator if you are unsure.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Can anyone enter a MOFILM competition?</strong><br />Anybody apart from employees / consultants
						of the brands or of MOFILM. You must be aged 16 or older (there are some restrictions as well
						for under-18s in some countries).
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>How do I enter a MOFILM competition?</strong><br />All you need to do is register with MOFILM
						and you can start participating in our competitions.  The prizes and briefs vary, so it's worth opting
						into our newsletter or checking back from time to time.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>What is the MOFILM:Labs Programme?</strong><br />MOFILM:Labs is our training programme. MOFILM
						works with universities, film schools and corporate organisations to train people in making films in a
						workshop environment. For more information email <a href="mailto:labs@mofilm.com">labs@mofilm.com</a>
					</p>
